{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_11", "eventName": "淬火塵霾", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "11-14", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "一場相見", "storyInfo": "推進之王打開了通往諸王長眠之所的大門，維多利亞千年的歷史正奔向她。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g8_kingrestpath", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨大的門扉橫亙在地下空間之中，除了眾人的呼吸，沒有一點聲音。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，死亡總是寂靜的，再輝煌的王權都不能改變這一點。"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......諸王長眠之所。字面意思......是列王的墳墓。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#8$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們聽到什麼了嗎？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，除了我們幾個的呼吸聲。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毫無疑問，有什麼聲音正在這個空間中回蕩。"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是夢醒的呢喃，還是疲憊的呻吟？"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們在注視著自己。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“維多利亞”在注視著自己。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當她清楚地感受到這一點的時候，一種煩躁油然而生。"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們在期待什麼？他們在為自己構想一種怎樣的未來？"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她早就膩煩了被這些所追逐的日子。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她也已經很久沒有理會那隻如黃金一般的生物的呼喚了。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "金色的鬃毛......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，儘快完成這個任務。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島和自救軍會需要我們幫忙的。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "停下！", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#7$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地上的這些......是......", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......光線太暗，一開始我還以為是什麼上流社會的新奇裝飾。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#5$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些是血。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#5$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有交戰的痕跡。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一場無比慘烈的戰鬥......不，這是一片浸透死亡的泥潭。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "血跡。蜿蜒的血跡，一路爬行至道路盡頭的門縫背後，又或者，是從那扇巨大的門後爬出來的。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們早已乾涸，只留下暗紅色的扭曲殘漬，覆蓋在破碎的磚石之上。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被一同覆蓋的，還有殘損的箭頭，刀劍的碎片，法術轟擊留下的深坑。"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有一些更為巨大的痕跡，如同一道道能撕扯開此處靜謐的傷疤，裸露在神聖的大門上。"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然附近沒有留下任何一具屍體，但所有經歷過戰場的人都能輕易地想像出這裡曾經發生過什麼。"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩群人抱著必死的信念而戰，很顯然，他們都遂了願。"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從血跡顏色來看，好幾年前的事了。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾年前......難道是......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是薩卡茲。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死在這裡的是薩卡茲。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能認出他們的武器。這些武器......與當年襲擊塔樓騎士的薩卡茲戰士使用的是同一批。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......與現在外面的薩卡茲士兵用的不同。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不一樣。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲後來佩戴的刀劍都是海布里區的軍工廠裡造出來的，和維多利亞軍隊用的制式武器很接近。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們沒這麼粗糙。也遠遠沒有......這麼野蠻。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還記得......這些生銹的刀砍向我同僚的身體的聲音。它們很重，在劈裂甲胄之前，會先震斷骨頭。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "達格達，你還好嗎？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我沒事。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#3$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果僅僅只是看見這些痕跡就會讓我止步不前的話，我大概無法度過逃離倫蒂尼姆後的任何一個夜晚。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......維娜，情況出乎我們的意料。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些聲音攪得她頭痛。"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們在催促。他們在訴說。"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸王之息還在裡面。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保持冷靜，繼續前行。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g8_kingrestpath", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與這些薩卡茲戰鬥的人是誰？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無法判斷。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一方沒有留下任何痕跡？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也有可能是我沒有見過的痕跡。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鉛踝先生，你當雇傭兵多久了？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "差一個月十四年。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一定見過出產自大部分國家地區的武器。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "見過，但見不全。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是個普通的雇傭兵，沒怎麼見過各國精銳部隊的武器。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是見過的話，我活不到現在。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根，因陀羅，你們退回到通道之外警戒。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像以前一樣，確保撤退的線路，對吧？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願我不會錯過什麼精彩的橋段。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王，我們不能貿然繼續前進......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#9$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你能聽到發生在我們頭頂的戰鬥嗎，達格達？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽不見。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#10$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能。這樣的震動......我能想像得到。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能空著手回去，達格達。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這把劍能阻止這一切，哪怕僅僅只是讓犧牲與屠戮的腳步放緩些......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我就會去做。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會把這視為責任，這只是......一次小小的行動。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和敲掉來找麻煩的打手的門牙沒什麼不同。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛，你說的。走到這一步以後，我們已經不剩下什麼回頭的機會了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g7_subway", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看起來不是很痛快。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，這可是在王宮地下打架的機會！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願他們不會遇到什麼要動手的事情。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我可是為了你做了如此之大的犧牲啊。萬一你被人一箭放倒，總得有個人替你大喊一聲吧？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我的傻漢娜。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#8$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還記得第一次見到維娜的時候，她的樣子嗎？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#8$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼不記得。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她呀，拽得要命。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "摩根", "content": "明明那時候她個子小小的，脾氣卻很大，不怎麼愛說話。你甚至看不出她很生氣，可她動起手來..."}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "摩根", "content": "...哈哈，你說都是誰教會她打架的啊？"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她說是她的老師。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我原來以為她的老師是諾伯特區的哪位鬥毆大王。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來知道了維娜的出身，倒是說得通了，大概那位老師是個連腦子裡都塞滿了肌肉的騎士吧？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說真的，王子啊公主什麼的不都是穿著繡花裙跑都跑不快的類型嗎？什麼樣的老師會教她跟野獸似的打架啊？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，她第一次跟我們坦白身份的時候，我還以為她在開玩笑。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜才不會在這種關係到我們生死的問題上說笑。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原本我還以為只是些新崛起的幫派，想找我們格拉斯哥幫的麻煩。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果是針對王位繼承人的滅口行動？哈。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那幫傢伙的拳頭倒確實很硬。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當時覺得，陪著一位王儲冒險說不定比混跡街頭刺激得多，更何況，這位王儲還深得我心。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後不知不覺地，我們就跟著維娜逃出倫蒂尼姆，跟著她四處流浪，又跟著她回到這裡。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在......如果傳奇裡的英雄有得選，他們更樂意窩在沙發上喝一大口冰啤酒，不是嗎？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......後悔了？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#10$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼可能，我們都已經走到這了。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的回憶錄都開了頭了，我還想拿它大賺特賺一筆呢！《偉大的維娜陛下和她偉大的朋友們》，只差出版商找上門了。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就你肚子裡那點可憐的詞？算了吧！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜說了，挺好看的！", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在想......那間被我們砸壞了招牌的酒吧。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那可是維娜帶著我們打的第一場勝仗！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天晚上我們把酒窖裡的貨都喝光了。最後是貝爾德把我們一個接一個地背到卡車上，趁著警察過來之前，帶著我們逃回了家。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "混蛋，你又記錯了。背你的人分明是老子，貝爾德自己喝得以為馬桶是方向盤，你讓她開車試試？！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哈哈。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想的只是......不管在什麼地方，我們都還能像過去那樣，聚在一起做出點名堂對吧？哪怕只是從別的幫派那裡搶到一個酒吧也好。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "漢娜，你說......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回來這麼多天了，為什麼維娜一次都沒有主動提起過，要回格拉斯哥幫看看啊？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#2$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g8_kingrestpath", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......鑰匙。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "臨行之前，博士給了我這把鑰匙。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士說，這是凱爾希醫生透過談判得到的......只有它能打開我們面前這扇通往諸王長眠之所的門。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，我手中的這把鑰匙曾經屬於一位德拉克。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......阿勒黛。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道......另一把鑰匙在哪裡嗎？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一把鑰匙。"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屬於阿斯蘭王室的鑰匙，也能打開面前的這扇門。本該由她的父親交到她手上，她卻從未見過那把鑰匙的模樣。"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......為什麼突然問起這個？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#9$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛想起來，關於那把......諸王之息的另一個傳說。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“阿斯蘭帕夏手執利劍，試圖征服異邦的最後一塊土地。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“德拉克王的火焰法術奔向他，他的盔甲被燒成了莓果的顏色，一滴滴消失在火焰中。可他的劍比盔甲更硬。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“在刺入德拉克王的身體裡的那一刻，阿斯蘭帕夏手中的劍已只剩下一半。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“德拉克王因此保住性命，而阿斯蘭帕夏也失去了自己的右手。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“在德拉克與阿斯蘭簽訂盟約之後，這把劍亦被重鑄，自此成為開啟維多利亞數百年光輝的象徵。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的祖先......曾經差點殺死一位德拉克王。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我此刻正拿著紅龍後裔的鑰匙......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打開這扇通往諸王長眠之所的門。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......在這裡，無論是德拉克還是阿斯蘭——", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們都只是維多利亞。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_stonegateopen", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 5.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "門開了。"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這比她想像得更輕鬆，輕鬆到彷彿一切都早已準備好，只等著她這個輕輕的動作。"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g9_kingrest", "screenadapt": "showall", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在諸王長眠之所——"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞千年的歷史正奔向她，奔向離去又歸來的阿斯蘭。"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}